Create template for data input

Source: R/create_template_.R
create_template_.Rd

Create template for inputting data collected from sensory research

create_template_(.data, panelist, attribute)

Arguments

.data

output from generate_design function
panelist

column containing panelist information
attribute

a numeric value of number or sensory attributes or vector of sensory terms (lexicon)

Value

Returns a dataframe of sensory design with Panelist, Order, Product, and Sensory Attributes columns

Examples


design <- generate_design_(n_panelist = 20, product = 5, use_coding = TRUE)
